Name: Average time from Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION to Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR

Name: Average time between Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE and Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION

Name: Total resolution time of Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION
